Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.70,All,,0,0,0,,I realized why Ononoki-chan had always called me with such a weird nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:13.52,All,,0,0,0,,Why did she call me 'oni no onii-chan',\Nas in devilish-onii-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.82,All,,0,0,0,,The reason was very clear in the mirror world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.47,All,,0,0,0,,Reason being that, I really was a devil, from being a vampire before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.65,All,,0,0,0,,Even if the term isn't very respectful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.70,All,,0,0,0,,It is the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:30.75,All,,0,0,0,,Hachikuji-oneesan and Kushinawa-san both looked at me in the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.75,All,,0,0,0,,Though, if vampires did not exist in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.27,All,,0,0,0,,Vampires' traits should not exist either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:42.37,All,,0,0,0,,Therefore, this theory would not work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.05,All,,0,0,0,,Knowing I am a victim of a vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.57,All,,0,0,0,,But not acknowledging\Nthe existence of vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.25,All,,0,0,0,,Truly is contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.85,All,,0,0,0,,The truth is, vampires\Nindeed are non-existent in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.10,All,,0,0,0,,There is no reason to call me 'oni no onii-chan'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.27,All,,0,0,0,,But vampires not existing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:04.20,All,,0,0,0,,Does not equate to Oshino Shinobu not existing too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:09.45,All,,0,0,0,,The iron-blooded, hot-blooded, cold-blooded vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.22,All,,0,0,0,,Oddity-killer, Kiss-Shot Acerola-Orion Heart-Under-Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.67,All,,0,0,0,,The vampire that was once a human
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.82,All,,0,0,0,,Six hundred years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.25,All,,0,0,0,,She was a human
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.35,All,,0,0,0,,Aristocratic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.90,All,,0,0,0,,Making the castle her own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.80,All,,0,0,0,,Living inside it as a princess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.50,All,,0,0,0,,And that is her inner world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.95,All,,0,0,0,,Oshino Shinobu's opposite-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.57,All,,0,0,0,,Please don't be nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.52,All,,0,0,0,,Please lift up your head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.80,All,,0,0,0,,Araragi-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.55,All,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.05,All,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a vampire\Non the other side of the curtains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.17,All,,0,0,0,,Instead was an atmosphere created by only the noblest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.25,All,,0,0,0,,By reflex, I knelt down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:54.20,All,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for\Nspeaking with the curtain between us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.25,All,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for not showing\Nmy face whilst conversing with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:02.37,All,,0,0,0,,I have heard that you came\Nfrom another world. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.05,All,,0,0,0,,The Araragi-sama that came from another world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.25,All,,0,0,0,,In other words, the person that was familiar with me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.90,All,,0,0,0,,Is the same as you, but at the same time, not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.30,All,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.07,All,,0,0,0,,That's... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.88,All,,0,0,0,,The Araragi Koyomi of this world gets to be called as 'Araragi-sama'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.65,All,,0,0,0,,Always wanting to take off Ononoki-chan's panties
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.74,All,,0,0,0,,Pestering Oikura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.91,All,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out my character at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.51,All,,0,0,0,,Is it really my reverse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.65,All,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be Ougi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:35.85,All,,0,0,0,,It's an honour to converse with a human from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:41.51,All,,0,0,0,,Originally I was hoping to\Ndrink tea and share thoughts with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.40,All,,0,0,0,,But there isn't any time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.25,All,,0,0,0,,Araragi-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.37,All,,0,0,0,,The situation you're in right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.97,All,,0,0,0,,Please explain it in a way I would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:58.54,All,,0,0,0,,To you, I am untrustworthy,\Nand we do not know each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.85,All,,0,0,0,,However, do open up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:05.08,All,,0,0,0,,Even though I cannot guarantee your return\nI can at least help in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.85,All,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.82,All,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.91,All,,0,0,0,,You came from an interesting world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:21.74,All,,0,0,0,,From your perspective\Neverything must look fake right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:25.17,All,,0,0,0,,On the other hand... for me to be a vampire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.74,All,,0,0,0,,I would love to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.05,All,,0,0,0,,But for me, that is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.97,All,,0,0,0,,We probably think that the other party is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.45,All,,0,0,0,,Reminiscent of the moon\Nreflecting off the water's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:45.08,All,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\NI am not the same as the me in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.57,All,,0,0,0,,As the human counterpart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:51.00,All,,0,0,0,,I do not have the power of\Nopening up a portal to the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.74,All,,0,0,0,,How awe-inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.34,All,,0,0,0,,For Her Majesty to respond with such words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.20,All,,0,0,0,,I should be ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.71,All,,0,0,0,,I should take on the\Nresponsibility, and cut my own throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.28,All,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.97,All,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel the absolute need to cut my own throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.37,All,,0,0,0,,But, I think I can help you to devise a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.25,All,,0,0,0,,Just take it as some mere\Nrambling from an inexperienced person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.02,All,,0,0,0,,But please do hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.82,All,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.80,All,,0,0,0,,Heart-Under-Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.37,All,,0,0,0,,It might seem that\Ndevilish-oniichan can bear with it currently
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:28.45,All,,0,0,0,,He is indeed running out of\Ntime, please do make haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.45,All,,0,0,0,,I understand, Ononoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.45,All,,0,0,0,,Araragi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:37.42,All,,0,0,0,,I believe that it is in best interest\Nfor you to return to your own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.77,All,,0,0,0,,Only have I heard the words 'time is running out'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.17,All,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty had pin-pointed\Nthe exact thought in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.65,All,,0,0,0,,To think our thoughts are now identical
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.51,All,,0,0,0,,How superfluous is the honour\Nthat I have been bestowed upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:52.31,All,,0,0,0,,No... I am so foolish to have\Ninferred, what Her Majesty was pondering on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.37,All,,0,0,0,,How grand would the punishment be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.11,All,,0,0,0,,But why am I thinking in this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.28,All,,0,0,0,,In other words, because you exist in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.65,All,,0,0,0,,You will influence this world greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.65,All,,0,0,0,,Influence... Having a 'bad' influence\Nwould be a better way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.34,All,,0,0,0,,I know that it is disrespectful to say this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.65,All,,0,0,0,,However, Araragi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:21.08,All,,0,0,0,,You are likened to a great disaster to such a fragile world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.00,All,,0,0,0,,From my perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:29.48,All,,0,0,0,,It seemed like it was me\Nthat was drawn into a disaster instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.14,All,,0,0,0,,Suddenly Oshino Meme's words came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.97,All,,0,0,0,,'Your victimized look really pisses me off.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.60,All,,0,0,0,,That is what he would say on a number of occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.45,All,,0,0,0,,Whenever something would happen,\NI'd shift the problems onto apparitions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.92,All,,0,0,0,,Shifting the responsibility away from myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.92,All,,0,0,0,,That's what that specialist hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.30,All,,0,0,0,,I never had those intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:54.12,All,,0,0,0,,But again I adopted\N the similar thinking as I had done in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.10,All,,0,0,0,,That was what Her Majesty was trying to point out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.62,All,,0,0,0,,How should I give my gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.55,All,,0,0,0,,The world that you see as fake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.92,All,,0,0,0,,Filled with contradiction and illogicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.50,All,,0,0,0,,Has also balanced itself with its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:12.55,All,,0,0,0,,And you are shaking the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.87,All,,0,0,0,,Ononoki may look normal to you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:21.12,All,,0,0,0,,However for us, her personality dramatically mutated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.77,All,,0,0,0,,To be truthful, I am starting to be influenced also
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.60,All,,0,0,0,,Who was the Araragi-sama I had been so familiar with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.77,All,,0,0,0,,My memories are starting to blur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.47,All,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.57,All,,0,0,0,,How did I behave in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.72,All,,0,0,0,,Anymore carelessness...\Nand I would need to take my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:43.55,All,,0,0,0,,Guilt is slowly tormenting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.32,All,,0,0,0,,Sorry but I cannot tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.77,All,,0,0,0,,I-is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.82,All,,0,0,0,,Because you have forgotten it and cannot recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.17,All,,0,0,0,,That is not it, it has not got to that point yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.02,All,,0,0,0,,Though if we continue like this, it may become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.55,All,,0,0,0,,Ononoki, you should not say anything extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.87,All,,0,0,0,,Of course. I have not said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.75,All,,0,0,0,,Ononoki-chan had lied through her teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.10,All,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me that I stole your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.55,All,,0,0,0,,Or was that all a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.67,All,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, isn't that distasteful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.12,All,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that her jokes are going too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:25.07,All,,0,0,0,,B-but... I want to go back as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.27,All,,0,0,0,,That is what I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.72,All,,0,0,0,,But like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:30.90,All,,0,0,0,,I have no way of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.70,All,,0,0,0,,Even if I got anywhere near\Nto my only hope which is Kanbaru's large bath
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.57,All,,0,0,0,,I am still not one hundred percent\Nsure if I can get in contact\nwith the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:44.02,All,,0,0,0,,That's right! If I were to burden\NHer Majesty with such petty problems
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.90,All,,0,0,0,,The better option were to kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.77,All,,0,0,0,,So again, why do I want to kill myself so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.20,All,,0,0,0,,That's it Shinobu, we've ran out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.05,All,,0,0,0,,Time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.45,All,,0,0,0,,I will take him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.07,All,,0,0,0,,So, to conclude
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.10,All,,0,0,0,,How can you talk to Her Majesty like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.77,All,,0,0,0,,For Her to forgive, I'll use my death as...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.87,All,,0,0,0,,No... I had stood up without Her Majesty's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.15,All,,0,0,0,,This slave will have to carry even more sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.32,All,,0,0,0,,Die... Die... I must DIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.67,All,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.57,All,,0,0,0,,I will leave it to you Ononoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.27,All,,0,0,0,,No problem, I am used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.57,All,,0,0,0,,Araragi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.00,All,,0,0,0,,The path you are taking is indeed correct
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.72,All,,0,0,0,,However, this isn't enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.42,All,,0,0,0,,Do not think you can do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.97,All,,0,0,0,,Do acquire help from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.57,All,,0,0,0,,Just like how you gave me hope
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:35.57,All,,0,0,0,,Let us wish for someone\Nin this world to grant you hope too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.87,All,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Unlimited Rulebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:45.25,All,,0,0,0,,Talking to Her Majesty\Nfor long periods of time brings danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.82,All,,0,0,0,,To put it simply:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:50.55,All,,0,0,0,,Being under Her powerful\Ncharisma for too long makes you suicidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.10,All,,0,0,0,,She did mention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.07,All,,0,0,0,,'Time is running out' - and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.77,All,,0,0,0,,Wanting to die from being influenced by Her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.67,All,,0,0,0,,It's true that I accidentally knelt down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.27,All,,0,0,0,,But having such a presence, is no laughing matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:07.35,All,,0,0,0,,I assume that's why she stayed behind the curtains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.55,All,,0,0,0,,Correct, if you saw her beauty with your own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.20,All,,0,0,0,,Devilish-onii-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.92,All,,0,0,0,,You would probably gauge your own intestines out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.77,All,,0,0,0,,Why would I choose such a painful way to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.67,All,,0,0,0,,At least let me die less painfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:25.20,All,,0,0,0,,Was Shinobu like this when she was human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.72,All,,0,0,0,,The Genuine Princess, Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.97,All,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't think it was like that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.25,All,,0,0,0,,If we use your theory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.42,All,,0,0,0,,She would only be like that in Her inner world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.87,All,,0,0,0,,And not actually in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:42.12,All,,0,0,0,,She also mentioned that it is similar\Nto the moon reflecting off the water's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:49.17,All,,0,0,0,,Well, Shinobu's influence\Nmay have been too strong for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.77,All,,0,0,0,,It is quite clear why She was living by Herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:56.12,All,,0,0,0,,The almighty presence She has. makes people suicidal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.27,All,,0,0,0,,And that could easily be led to a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.62,All,,0,0,0,,Being a human, but exhibiting what a human can not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.35,All,,0,0,0,,Uhm, what did she say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.40,All,,0,0,0,,The path that I'm walking on is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:14.82,All,,0,0,0,,In other words, to pursue for\NKanbaru's bath as the way of returning to my world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.55,All,,0,0,0,,Is the right idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.40,All,,0,0,0,,That's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.97,All,,0,0,0,,But she did say you would have to find helpers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.12,All,,0,0,0,,Being alone would not get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.05,All,,0,0,0,,Even so
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:30.12,All,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to ask Her what she really meant right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:35.62,All,,0,0,0,,Mhm, your suicidal points\Nhave rised significantly, near breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.35,All,,0,0,0,,Until those points\Nhave dropped, it is safer to not go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.37,All,,0,0,0,,What the hell are suicidal points?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.77,All,,0,0,0,,It puts me on edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.97,All,,0,0,0,,Even using a relaxed tone to explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.47,All,,0,0,0,,Though it's true that we have\Nno time to wait for the points to decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.37,All,,0,0,0,,Helpers, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.72,All,,0,0,0,,To intrude onto\NKanbaru's property, we would need something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.62,All,,0,0,0,,That would attract Kanbaru's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.95,All,,0,0,0,,Something like that sounds impossible to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.25,All,,0,0,0,,Ononoki-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.25,All,,0,0,0,,Got anything in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.12,All,,0,0,0,,What kind of character could stop the Rainy Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.35,All,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, hmm....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:12.40,All,,0,0,0,,Possessing such destructive power and fighting prowess
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.85,All,,0,0,0,,Also knowing the situation we're in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.82,All,,0,0,0,,Acknowledging how devilish-onii-chan is feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.60,All,,0,0,0,,Having great crisis awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:23.20,All,,0,0,0,,With the motivation to solve any problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.32,All,,0,0,0,,To have on board professional knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.30,All,,0,0,0,,Lastly, to be able to escape from any situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.25,All,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.50,All,,0,0,0,,THAT'S YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.00,All,,0,0,0,,Koyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.32,All,,0,0,0,,The sun's rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.75,All,,0,0,0,,Get up you lazy sleepyhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:47.40,All,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm changing, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.72,All,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to see me change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.00,All,,0,0,0,,Koyomi is lewd as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.62,All,,0,0,0,,But if it's Koyomi, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.80,All,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.50,All,,0,0,0,,Don't d-do that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.62,All,,0,0,0,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:11.20,All,,0,0,0,,What Shinobu said about my bad influence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.85,All,,0,0,0,,By living together, in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.82,All,,0,0,0,,To think in terms of numbers,\NOikura spent the most time with me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.27,All,,0,0,0,,I might have influenced her the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.80,All,,0,0,0,,Ah, nii-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.47,All,,0,0,0,,We're going out to play with Sodachi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.80,All,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then have fun with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:35.25,All,,0,0,0,,What do you mean...\NNii-chan what are you to Sodachi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.50,All,,0,0,0,,See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:43.35,All,,0,0,0,,Ara, nii-sama, hope you are full of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.45,All,,0,0,0,,Joy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.07,All,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.40,All,,0,0,0,,Nope, washing my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.50,All,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it, no need to say more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:55.25,All,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan wants her\Ncute imouto to wash his face for him right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.95,All,,0,0,0,,Then prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.07,All,,0,0,0,,Prepare what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.15,All,,0,0,0,,I am washing my own face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.97,All,,0,0,0,,Is it not okay if I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.15,All,,0,0,0,,Since when did we progress into a shoujo manga setting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.57,All,,0,0,0,,And why am I the female protagonist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.15,All,,0,0,0,,I'm coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.72,All,,0,0,0,,Let's get you clean as a whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.75,All,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:18.52,All,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan. Use your mouth\Nto fetch the soap from the soap box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.75,All,,0,0,0,,Then put it in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:24.17,All,,0,0,0,,Why should I get the soap for you\Nwhile getting accused of being in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.65,All,,0,0,0,,And with my mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.20,All,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.20,All,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you might go blind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.17,All,,0,0,0,,There's definitely that risk\Nwhen you used an excess amount of soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.42,All,,0,0,0,,But why give such dangerous\Nwarnings when you're just washing my face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.32,All,,0,0,0,,I have to, this is my first time washing someone else's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:49.67,All,,0,0,0,,My point is that, I may accidentally\Npierce your pupils with my fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.50,All,,0,0,0,,If it's warnings like that, its too late to tell me it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.45,All,,0,0,975,,{\b1\u0}Eat my bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.87,All,,0,0,0,,Hmm, this isn't good enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:59.12,All,,0,0,0,,Should I use Sodachi-chan's\Nface wash without her permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.92,All,,0,0,0,,Let's not do that-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:07.80,All,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, let's finish it here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.90,All,,0,0,0,,Let's splash the face a little
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.05,All,,0,0,0,,I am not taking fault for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.07,All,,0,0,0,,I did warn you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.07,All,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do as said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.02,All,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.90,All,,0,0,0,,Anyways the water was gone,\Nthere's nothing you could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.05,All,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem problematic either
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.85,All,,0,0,0,,Don't be too conscious of it-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.55,All,,0,0,0,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.70,All,,0,0,0,,That is actually quite important
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:51.47,All,,0,0,0,,The portal to the other world\Ndoesn't have to be in monkey-onee-chan's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.05,All,,0,0,0,,It's actually in the sink of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.40,All,,0,0,0,,Don't say 'our house' so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.85,All,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Sodachi onee-chan what you just said
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:00.95,All,,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.02,All,,0,0,0,,Don't bully Oikura into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.70,All,,0,0,0,,But to be fair it was only for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.20,All,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was seeing things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.25,All,,0,0,0,,I couldn't recreate what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.82,All,,0,0,0,,I have no clue as why it would appear either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.22,All,,0,0,0,,Well the first time was the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.92,All,,0,0,0,,Second: the mirroring water
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.72,All,,0,0,0,,They happened in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.40,All,,0,0,0,,The meaning of it is different though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.92,All,,0,0,0,,The similarity was that you were washing your face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:29.60,All,,0,0,0,,That could be the condition for the portal to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.07,All,,0,0,0,,What kind of condition is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.57,All,,0,0,0,,I could wash my face when I'm showering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.62,All,,0,0,0,,Anyways, how ever you look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.02,All,,0,0,0,,The reflected 'me' was\Neither laughing or not coordinating with me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.07,All,,0,0,0,,But it didn't seem like important details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.07,All,,0,0,0,,If we had the same objective
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.60,All,,0,0,0,,The other me could call for\NShinobu or get someone that could to contact her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.92,All,,0,0,0,,Hmmph, that is true
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:55.85,All,,0,0,0,,Then it looks like today's mission would be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.20,All,,0,0,0,,Hopefully it'll be solved today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.35,All,,0,0,0,,I did spend a day unwillingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.40,All,,0,0,0,,Oikura is starting to show some bad signs too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.10,All,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.97,All,,0,0,0,,That change could be reverted with a simple method.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.42,All,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.02,All,,0,0,0,,A simple method?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.12,All,,0,0,0,,Yep, extremely simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.32,All,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.67,All,,0,0,0,,Could say it is a variant\Nof the Copenhagen Interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:29.02,All,,0,0,0,,'Copenhagen Interpretation'?\NDidn't you say it was simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.82,All,,0,0,0,,What was it again, Quantum Mechanics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.12,All,,0,0,0,,Awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.02,All,,0,0,0,,I meant "Copernicus' Revolvement".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:39.32,TL Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: コパルニクスの転回 (Copernicus' Revolvement) can be used to exemplify the way of dealing with things from a totally different perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.10,All,,0,0,0,,Who the hell knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.22,All,,0,0,0,,Don't get something so similar wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:45.72,All,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, even though Copernicus' Revolvement\nand the Copenhagen Interpretation are very far apart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:49.02,All,,0,0,0,,We could say this is a case of Copernicus' Revolvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.65,All,,0,0,0,,If onii-chan gives up on returning to the original world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.85,All,,0,0,0,,Then there wouldn't be any problem staying here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:56.95,All,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.47,All,,0,0,0,,There's that plan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.37,All,,0,0,0,,You're so clever, Ononoki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.50,All,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's no need for us to intrude Kanbaru's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.70,All,,0,0,0,,...Wait, in what way could this solve the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.15,All,,0,0,0,,If I continue to stay in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.27,All,,0,0,0,,That's because you've decided to return
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.65,All,,0,0,0,,In other words, onii-chan didn't intend to be here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.90,All,,0,0,0,,Like a transfer student that\Nuses their local dialect to boast about their homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.97,All,,0,0,0,,Worsening the atmosphere in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.42,All,,0,0,0,,What kind of example is this? Makes me feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.25,All,,0,0,0,,If onii-chan gives up on\Ngoing back, also opening up to this world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.37,All,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan will be influenced by this world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.65,All,,0,0,0,,Be pressured-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.27,All,,0,0,0,,Then onii-chan will revert to what he was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.95,All,,0,0,0,,Though strictly speaking, it'll be a compromise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:45.02,All,,0,0,0,,For us it'll seem that you are the same as you always were
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.52,All,,0,0,0,,Monkey-onee-chan won't attack you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:52.85,All,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't get near her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.27,All,,0,0,0,,If you made your mind up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.05,All,,0,0,0,,You can start living a sweet life with Sodachi-onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.45,All,,0,0,0,,Don't say it like that's my ultimate goal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.97,All,,0,0,0,,Like I'm staying in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.95,All,,0,0,0,,Just because I wanted a sweet, lovely life with Oikura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.12,All,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it is a plan to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.37,All,,0,0,0,,For Ononoki-chan to have\Ncome up with this plan, I'll apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.57,All,,0,0,0,,Because to live in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:23.65,All,,0,0,0,,I will have to leave a lot of\Nthings behind in the world I came from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.95,All,,0,0,0,,If I still have hope, I will still pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.35,All,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to risk my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.25,All,,0,0,0,,But I will have to risk my life too
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.35,All,,0,0,0,,W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.37,All,,0,0,0,,That's alright, I'm dead anyways
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.90,All,,0,0,0,,I'm just mentioning it. Just asking that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.12,All,,0,0,0,,It's not like the plan is flawless or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:53.05,All,,0,0,0,,If devilish-onii-chan did get used to the status quo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:57.45,All,,0,0,0,,What will happen if the real Araragi Koyomi came?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.00,All,,0,0,0,,The real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.07,All,,0,0,0,,I guess for the people in this world it'll be the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.60,All,,0,0,0,,But don't label me like some fake counterfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.70,All,,0,0,0,,Two of the same person that existed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.65,All,,0,0,0,,Doppelgänger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.70,All,,0,0,0,,It'll destroy the balance of the world for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.97,All,,0,0,0,,So where did Araragi Koyomi really disappear off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.80,All,,0,0,0,,Did he really switch places with onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:25.75,All,,0,0,0,,We're here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.07,All,,0,0,0,,So as planned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.22,All,,0,0,0,,I will try to buy some time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.60,All,,0,0,0,,You can explore around the house a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.22,All,,0,0,0,,Even bathe a little if you want onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.40,All,,0,0,0,,How can I be that relaxed now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.85,All,,0,0,0,,There will be plenty of time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.12,All,,0,0,0,,If it's me, not only 5 minutes
